## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="463a9-102"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ExternalDataExchangeAttribute>로 표시된 로컬 통신 인터페이스는 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ExternalDataEventArgs> 활동과 함께 워크플로에서 해당 이벤트를 처리하기 위해 인터페이스 정의의 <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity>에서 파생되는 형식을 선언해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="463a9-102">A local communication interface marked with <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ExternalDataExchangeAttribute> must declare a type that derives from <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ExternalDataEventArgs> in the interface definition for the corresponding event to be handled in a workflow with a <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> activity.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="463a9-103"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ExternalDataEventArgs>에서 상속되는 이벤트 클래스는 `:base(instanceId)` 생성자를 사용하는 생성자를 구현해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="463a9-103">An event class that inherits from <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.ExternalDataEventArgs> must implement a constructor that uses the `:base(instanceId)` constructor.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="463a9-104">또한 다음 코드에서처럼 새 이벤트 클래스를 `Serializable`로 표시해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="463a9-104">In addition, the new event class must be marked as `Serializable` as shown in the following code.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[Serializable]  
public class TaskEventArgs : ExternalDataEventArgs  
{  
    private string orderName;  
  
    public TaskEventArgs(Guid instanceId, string id)  
        :base(instanceId)  
    {  
        orderName = id;  
    }  
  
    public string Id  
    {  
        get { return orderName; }  
        set { orderName = value; }  
    }  
}  
```
